text: Somatidia antarctica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by White in 1846, originally under the genus Parmena. It feeds on Dacrydium cupressinum.BioLib.cz - Somatidia antarctica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1846
